      <title>中国派出创纪录的 111 架战机飞越台海要冲</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-15/china-sent-a-record-111-warplanes-across-key-line-with-taiwan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国创纪录地有 111 架战机飞越台湾海峡美国划定的边界，凸显北京对民主政府施加的军事压力之大。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-15/china-sent-a-record-111-warplanes-across-key-line-with-taiwan</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 15 Oct 2024 02:41:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国军方警告将对台湾施加更大压力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-15/china-s-military-warns-it-ll-slap-taiwan-with-even-more-pressure</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国军方警告称，必要时将加大对台湾的压力，这一迹象表明，这个受美国支持的拥有 2,300 万人口的民主国家，可能会重复本周初的激烈演习。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-15/china-s-military-warns-it-ll-slap-taiwan-with-even-more-pressure</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 15 Oct 2024 02:22:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普宾夕法尼亚活动因观众晕倒而被迫取消</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-14/trump-harris-pitch-economic-plans-to-pennsylvania-swing-voters</link>
      <description><![CDATA[共和党总统候选人唐纳德·特朗普原本计划在费城郊区一个闷热的市政厅举行竞选演讲，但由于周一多名观众晕倒并需要就医，演讲提前结束并变成了一场即兴舞会。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-14/trump-harris-pitch-economic-plans-to-pennsylvania-swing-voters</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 14 Oct 2024 23:34:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特鲁多指责印度外交官涉嫌暴力犯罪</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-14/trudeau-accuses-indian-diplomats-of-links-to-criminal-violence</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大总理贾斯汀·特鲁多指责印度外交官支持针对加拿大人的刑事骚扰和暴力行为，这进一步升级了去年开始的争端，当时他暗示印度特工参与了不列颠哥伦比亚省一名加拿大锡克教活动人士的谋杀案。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-14/trudeau-accuses-indian-diplomats-of-links-to-criminal-violence</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 14 Oct 2024 23:06:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国资金为东欧提供抵御布鲁塞尔影响的对冲手段</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-14/chinese-cash-offers-eastern-europe-a-hedge-against-the-influence-of-brussels</link>
      <description><![CDATA[斯洛伐克总理借鉴了奥尔班的策略——向北京和莫斯科示好，以减少对欧盟的依赖]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-14/chinese-cash-offers-eastern-europe-a-hedge-against-the-influence-of-brussels</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 14 Oct 2024 23:00:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新加坡前总理儿子试图拆除族长的住宅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-14/singapore-ex-premier-s-son-seeks-to-demolish-patriarch-s-home</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新加坡首任总理李光耀的小儿子正在向当局寻求拆除其已故父亲的住宅的许可，这是围绕该国最引人注目的房产命运的激烈争斗的最新升级。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-14/singapore-ex-premier-s-son-seeks-to-demolish-patriarch-s-home</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 14 Oct 2024 22:56:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>据《华盛顿邮报》报道，内塔尼亚胡同意限制对伊朗的打击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-14/netanyahu-agrees-to-limit-strike-on-iran-washington-post</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据《华盛顿邮报》报道，以色列总理本雅明内塔尼亚胡同意将以色列对伊朗10月1日导弹袭击的报复限制在军事目标上。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-14/netanyahu-agrees-to-limit-strike-on-iran-washington-post</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 14 Oct 2024 22:15:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
